channel.title: How do i change starting spot
channel.description:
i have a 517 surver and you start of in varrock big bank, then u can do ::pvp to go to pvp which also teles u to varrock big bank, so how do i make it that you log in and start off in the pvp bank?
thanks[br][br][size=1]Posted on: November 14, 2009, 06:39:03 pm[/size][hr]please?

item.title: How do i change starting spot

item.description:

[quote=“jamessemple, post:5, topic:314194”][quote author=Mod Franklin link=topic=410671.msg3029446#msg3029446 date=1258254662]

for teleports search in clikingmost.java and client.java

it’s a 517 u wanker, learn to read before u post.[/quote]
